260
00:28:45,370 --> 00:28:47,690
What promise?

261
00:28:47,690 --> 00:28:49,950
Just in the case...

262
00:28:51,530 --> 00:28:53,300
If

263
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:56,060
I change.

264
00:28:56,060 --> 00:28:57,820
Change?

265
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,260
How?

266
00:29:00,260 --> 00:29:03,980
There's a bug living inside a person's heart.

267
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:09,310
If that bug takes and swallows me

268
00:29:10,630 --> 00:29:14,670
and if I'm not who I used to be,

269
00:29:15,850 --> 00:29:17,520
if I change to that...

270
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:19,990
I will kill you.

271
00:29:19,990 --> 00:29:21,810
Good.

272
00:29:21,810 --> 00:29:28,400
