412
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:32,180
General!

413
00:40:33,730 --> 00:40:36,730
I will earnestly ask you again.

414
00:40:39,900 --> 00:40:44,650
Can't you just accept those people who are Lee In Gyeom's faction members?

415
00:40:46,650 --> 00:40:50,220
