416
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:52,800
Look here, Sam Bong!

417
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:56,870
Those people leached off Lee In Gyeom and for the past decade

418
00:40:56,870 --> 00:41:01,410
have persecuted the people. They're not any different than Hong In Bang and Gil Tae Mi.

419
00:41:01,410 --> 00:41:04,810
What are you saying I should do with those people?

420
00:41:04,810 --> 00:41:07,150
General Choi Yeong.

421
00:41:08,330 --> 00:41:12,360
Join forces with those people and aim for General Choi Yeong.

422
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:15,260
What?

423
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:16,700
What?

424
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:22,950
I said that Lee Seong Gye will eventually attack you, General.

425
00:41:22,950 --> 00:41:26,160
With the same mindset, Lee Seong Gye

426
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:28,980
