427
00:41:28,980 --> 00:41:32,620
That Lee Seong Gye would attack me? Why?

428
00:41:32,620 --> 00:41:35,810
Lee Seong Gye trusts and follows you.
 (Lee In Gyeom) 

429
00:41:35,810 --> 00:41:41,230
Also, he still looks weak right now.

430
00:41:42,150 --> 00:41:46,890
The problem is Lee Seong Gye's desire.

